column2: SELECT s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, m.mangaID, m.objra FROM #upload u JOIN SpecObjAll s ON (s.plate = u.up_plate AND s.mjd = u.up_mjd AND s.fiberID = u.up_fiber) JOIN mangaPipe3D m ON (m.objra - s.ra < # AND s.ra - m.objra > #) where m.objra - s.ra < # AND s.ra - m.objra > # ##', @log = #, @filter = #
